1. Submissions must be typed, not hand written

2. They must fall in line with the dates supplied (if there are any)

3. Times New Roman – font size 12

4. Black text, white background

5. Submit via Email only

6. Submissions must include your name and contact details, Accurate word count and Genre

7. A synopsis or blurb should appear with your manuscript, this includes a short summary of plot as well as motivation for why this book is amazing (This may include plot twists and ending as motivation)

8. Submissions must not exceed 50 000 words

9. “End” must appear on final page, any notes after that must be limited to half a page

10. Should you not hear back in 4-6 weeks consider your application unsuccessful
